  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"font-style:italic;padding-left:1em;display:flow-root;\" class=\"poem\">\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Smith_(the_Seven)\" title=\"Smith (the Seven)\">Smith</a>, he labors day and night,<br />\nto put the world of men to right.<br />\nWith hammer, plow, and fire bright,<br />\nhe builds for little children.\n</p>\n</div><p> —<a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Tarly\" title=\"Samwell Tarly\">Samwell Tarly</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_46\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 46\">Chapter 46</a>, Samwell III.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405173340\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.009 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 139/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8468/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 376/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 182/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 1/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 859/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    5.527      1 -total\n 78.76%    4.353      1 Template:Ref\n 54.24%    2.998      1 Template:Ref/core\n 20.15%    1.114      1 Template:Lyrics\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:26930-0!canonical an